    <p>6.2. Users are expressly referred in the context of the Facebook consent dialog to this data collection and the data shared by Facebook with us (e.g. public profile, friends list, e-mail address and "Like" information, only if these data elements are viewable by the public according to your Facebook privacy settings) through the Service.</p>
